%% MyAIStorybook - Activity Diagram: Complete Story Generation Workflow

graph TD
    Start([Start]) --> A1[User: Enter story prompt]
    A1 --> A2[User: Select generation options]
    A2 --> A3[User: Click Weave Magic]
    
    A3 --> B1[Frontend: Send generation request]
    B1 --> C1[Backend: Receive prompt]
    C1 --> C2{Prompt valid?}
    
    C2 -->|No| C3[Return error message]
    C3 --> D1[Frontend: Display error]
    D1 --> Stop1([Stop])
    
    C2 -->|Yes| C4[PromptAgent: Enhance prompt]
    C4 --> E1[DirectorAgent: Initialize pipeline]
    
    E1 --> F1[WriterAgent: Generate story structure]
    F1 --> F2[WriterAgent: Create title and setting]
    F2 --> F3[WriterAgent: Develop characters]
    F3 --> F4[WriterAgent: Write 3 scenes]
    F4 --> F5[WriterAgent: Generate image descriptions]
    
    F5 --> G1[ReviewerAgent: Review story draft]
    G1 --> G2[ReviewerAgent: Check age-appropriateness]
    G2 --> G3[ReviewerAgent: Evaluate coherence]
    G3 --> G4[ReviewerAgent: Generate feedback]
    
    G4 --> H1[EditorAgent: Apply feedback]
    H1 --> H2[EditorAgent: Refine story text]
    H2 --> H3[EditorAgent: Ensure JSON validity]
    H3 --> H4[EditorAgent: Generate PDF export]
    
    H4 --> I1{Generate images?}
    
    I1 -->|Yes| J1[ImageAgent: Generate Scene 1]
    I1 -->|Yes| J2[ImageAgent: Generate Scene 2]
    I1 -->|Yes| J3[ImageAgent: Generate Scene 3]
    
    J1 --> J4[Save all images]
    J2 --> J4
    J3 --> J4
    J4 --> K1[Backend: Save story to database]
    
    I1 -->|No| K1
    
    K1 --> K2[EvaluationAgent: Evaluate quality in background]
    K1 --> K3[Backend: Prepare response]
    K3 --> L1[Frontend: Receive story data]
    
    L1 --> L2[Frontend: Initialize story display]
    L2 --> L3[Frontend: Render page navigation]
    L3 --> L4[Frontend: Load images if available]
    
    L4 --> M1[User: View generated story]
    M1 --> M2{Want to chat?}
    
    M2 -->|Yes| N1[User: Select character]
    N1 --> N2[ChatbotAgent: Generate responses]
    N2 --> N3[User: Continue chatting]
    N3 --> M3{Want to export?}
    
    M2 -->|No| M3
    
    M3 -->|Yes| O1[User: Download PDF]
    O1 --> Stop2([Stop])
    
    M3 -->|No| Stop2
    
    style Start fill:#90ee90
    style Stop1 fill:#ffcccb
    style Stop2 fill:#ffcccb
    style C2 fill:#ffd700
    style I1 fill:#ffd700
    style M2 fill:#ffd700
    style M3 fill:#ffd700
